{"id": "1431510224472248320", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "393585313618067456", "author_name": "katesthio", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ogier: Shielder/Strength Gen/2 turn Vuln\nCeleste: Healer/Weakness Application/One Free Revive\nSanga: More Shield = More Damage Exalt/Shield(but expensive af)\nTulu: Dps Tentacle Dmg/AOE Dmg/Burst Dmg Amp Exalt/All cards if not played(or discarded), 1 tentacle slap\nMurphy: Weakness and Vuln Application scaling of Tentacle Dmg, A bit of Skey, 0 cost shield but gain sacrifice, Exalt cuts dmg in half but takes half of the dmg as sacrifice, Sacrifice is dot damage taken at end of turn and the reduce the “Sacrifice” stacks by half", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T05:10:33.688000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
