{"id": "1431778694417874955", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "179235663160279040", "author_name": "ellumi", "author_bot": false, "content": "i think building poision (or situtationally counter) with daffodil ult is better, the 4 cost is only good early in a boss fight (to build str or vulnerable/2arthi back, 500keyflare) or to finish off enemies in the exploration.\nalso worth noting try to get all kills as daffodil since she scales when killing enemies, and replace the 2nd WoD to the one that gives her aliemus when she kills an enemy, that way your ult that sweeps low health enemies can almost insta recharge the ult itself again.\n\nalso when duping with thais ult, its a lot more worth it to duplicate her own cards (the keyflare vul/weakness/embryo one or the str+aliemus one, at E2 thais they will go to 0 cost and build up enough embryo for daffodil to recharge and get a crit boost for the turn. selling winkle's discard defense card can be pretty useful as well, but since the comp doesnt have another defender i would experiment with and without it first", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T22:57:21.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["196755044685709313"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431626847778640004", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
